These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
Game: go, mah-jongg
1. Game:go is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| Game   | mah-jongg | go |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-2::.
